attachments.title: HackPDX Winter Hackathon @ Airbnb Portland
attachments.text: We're back! Â Join us for the Winter 2015 Hackathon at Airbnb Portland! The theme is education, but feel free to hack on something PDX related or anything at all. There will be food for everyone and prizes for the best hacks, so come with a team, make one here, or fly solo to gain everlasting fame as the creator of the next Instagram for IOT BigData SoMoLo Toasters. Please RSVP if you're planning on attending; space is limited and you must be on the list to get in! Schedule, sponsors, and prize list TBA.
